========================================================================

Judge t's Arguments:

When lee amended the budget, e did not mention the Treasuror's salary. As
the amendment explicitly defined all changed salaries, it is the court's
opinion that this was only a partial amendment of the budget, which did
not modify any salaries which were not mentioned, therefore the
Treasuror's salary retains its old value.

========================================================================